1. Installed nvm (Node Version Manager) with the following command:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed the terminal using the "exit" command, then reopened it.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using nvm:
   nvm install 20.16

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 globally using npm:
   npm install -g sass@3.7.4
